c: 2
v: 126
t: "Khumbulani okokuba uIbrâhîm wathi: “Nkosi yethu yenza esi sixeko ibe sisixeko sokhuseleko. Unike abantu baso iziqhamo (ingakumbi) abakholwayo kuAllâh nakwiMini yokuGqibela.” UAllâh Waphendula: “Lowo ungakholwayo Ndiya kumyeka ahlale enelisekile okwethutyana, Ndize Ndimnyanzelise ukuba angene eMlilweni wokumngcungcuthekisa. Hayi ububi besiphelo solo hambo.”"